</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the connector from the clock assembly.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Using a service wire, connect terminals 23 (PAON) and 17 (P-AB) of connector B.</ptxt>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Do not forcibly insert a service wire into the terminals of the connector when connecting.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Measure the resistance according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt>
